conference calls violates sunshine laws for meetings and
proceedings. By Tina Kelley.
</P>
<P>
   With photo.
</P>
<P>
   CIR-COMPUTER-COLUMN (Undated) _ How to protect yourself from
E-mail viruses. By Peter H. Lewis.
</P>
<P>
   CIR-DANCER-DNA (Undated) _ Dancer DNA, which lets you create
organisms, watch them evolve, and make them dance. By J.C. Herz.
</P>
<P>
   CIR-HITCHCOCK (Undated) _ Hitchcock program for fans and serious
students. By Shelly Freierman.
</P>
<P>
   CIR-COMPUTER-DOUBTS (Undated) _ Academics who have serious
