diners devour fish platters under the scrutiny of fish peering in
at them through portholes. By Deborah Sontag.
</P>
<P>
   With Photo.
</P>
<P>
   MAYA-LIN (Clinton, Tenn.) _ For eighteen years Maya Lin's
reputation has been etched in stone. ``I need a body of work to
come out for people to realize how serious I am about this
discipline,'' Ms. Lin, 39, said. By Fred Bernstein.
</P>
