<HEADER>
A2550 &Cx1f; taf-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-KOSOVO-ADVISORY-NYT &LR;      04-01 0538
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-KOSOVO-ADVISORY-NYT </SLUG>
  
(gm)
<TEXT>
<P>
   The New York Times is planning a five-page package of stories,
photos and graphics on the continuing crisis in Kosovo:
</P>
<P>
   KOSOVO-RDP (Washington) _ The ledeall, focusing on the captured
American soldiers; other developments. By Francis X. Clines.
</P>
<P>
   With map.
</P>
<P>
