<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-01 13:57 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2552 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-VIDEO-COLUMN-WRITETHR     04-01 0779
