   MARKET (New York) _ At midday, the industrial average was down
11 points and the Nasdaq index was up 5 points. Elsewhere, prices
increased 3.1 percent in Tokyo and 1.2 percent in Hong Kong. They
gained 0.8 percent in Frankfurt and 0.6 percent in London. The
Brazilian and Mexican markets were closed. On the American debt
market, the long bond was off 29/32 point. By Robert D. Hershey.
