from around the world converge to attend comedies, dramas and
musicals by George Bernard Shaw and his contemporaries.
905-468-2172.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  May-November: Stratford Festival. Something for everyone, from
classic Elizabethan theater to contemporary shows. 519-273-1600.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  May 14-24: Canadian Tulip Festival, Ottawa. The largest tulip
fest in the world celebrates the opening of the new American
embassy in Ottawa with an eclectic mix of Canadian and American
headliners from New York swing bands and Louisiana Cajun-style
music. 613-567-5757.
