   www.gov.nb.ca/tourism
</P>
<P>
   1-800-561-0123
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  June 16-20: Atlantic Aquaculture Fair, St. Andrews. Includes a
trade show, a salmon barbecue, twilight cruises and the sea
farmers' market. 506-529-4578.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  July 2-11: Shediac Lobster Festival. This popular fest marks
its 50th anniversary with activities including a lobster-eating
contest and a giant parade. 506-532-7000.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  July 17-25: Festival Western de Saint-Quentin, St. Quentin.
The Maritimes' largest western festival with a rodeo, parade,
children's activities and more. 506-235-1999.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  Aug. 6-15: Festival by the Sea, St. John. Arts festival
featuring mostly free performances. 506-632-0086.
</P>
