   PRINCE EDWARD ISLAND
</P>
<P>
   www.peiplay.com
</P>
<P>
   1-888-734-7529
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  June 22-Oct. 10: The Charlottetown Festival. The musical
``Anne of Green Gables'' and free outdoor performances are
highlights of this summerlong event. 902-566-1267.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  July 17-18: Rollo Bay Fiddlers Festival. The 23rd annual
edition of this festival features concerts all weekend, rain or
shine. 902-687-2584.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  Aug. 20-22: Lucy Maud Montgomery Festival, Cavendish. Various
activities celebrate the 125th birthday of the ``Anne of Green
Gables'' author with readings, music and dancing. 902-963-2149.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  Sept. 17-19, PEI Shellfish Festival, Charlottetown. A
celebration of Malpeque oysters and Island Blue mussels with
tastings, music, contests and storytelling. 902-566-9748.
