<P>
   UNDATED _ Fans and producers of ``Vengeance Unlimited'' are
asking critics to take another look at the ABC show, in hopes of
saving it. The campaign taps into the unfortunate realities of hype
from the news media and the networks: Our impatience with new shows
actually keeps good programs from getting the chance to develop an
audience. By KEN PARISH PERKINS. Story will move in ``e''
entertainment category. &QL; 
