<P>
   BIZBOOKS-REVIEWS &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ Show business can be big business _ even for companies
that make a living outside of the Hollywood spotlight. That's the
message delivered by an entertainment industry consultant in a new
book called ``The Entertainment Economy: How Mega-Media Forces are
Transforming our Lives'' (Times Books, $25, 336 pages). By TERESA
MCUSIC. Story has moved in ``f'' financial category. &QL; 
