 &UR; GUMSHOE &LR;  _ Move over, Sherlock Holmes, Hercule Poirot and Sam
Spade.
</P>
<P>
   A new breed of investigator has arrived in American workplaces _
outside professionals who are hired by companies to sleuth out the
truth of employee complaints about sexual harassment,
discrimination or embezzlement. By Ilana DeBare
</P>
<P>
   &UR; GUMSIDE  &LR; _ Employment investigators see the seamy side of work
life: harassment, discrimination, office politics and paranoia.
</P>
<P>
