<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-01 20:09 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2991 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HEARST-NEWS-BUDGET-2N     04-01 0741
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-HEARST-NEWS-BUDGET-2NDLD-WRITETHRU-HNS </SLUG>
  
 Thursday, April 1, 1999    
 Editors     
<TEXT>
<P>
