<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-CAPTURED-GONZALES-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Friends of POW pray for the best
 &HT;    By Mike Kelley
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
