   (NYT15) ORVIETO, Italy -- April 1, 1999 -- ADV. FOR SUN., APRIL
4 -- MILLENIUM-ORVIETO-COX, 4-01 -- Parishioners worship during
Saturday evening Mass at St. Andrew and St. Bartholomew Church in
Orvieto. It was so cold in the small parish church that worshippers
kept their coats on and small space heathers were placed in the
aisles. (Jean Shifrin/Atlanta Journal Constitution Photo)
